# Normalise line endings to LF in the working tree on every platform.
#
# Without this, Git converts to CRLF on Windows checkouts while CI runs on
# Linux with LF. Prettier is configured for LF, so `npm run format:check`
# would pass in CI and fail on a fresh Windows clone — a confusing failure
# that has nothing to do with the code.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files must never be converted.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
